1.0.name: wordpress/websimon-tables
1.0.description:
Websimon Tables lets you create and design tables within your wordpress admin panel. No knowledge about php, HTML or CSS is needed. You can create as many tables as you wish and create a unique design for each table. You include the tables in your post or pages using a short and simple shortcode. The tables can contain images or any type of html code so you can extend them for your own needs.

If you want to see more information, demos or screenshots of this plugin please visit http://websimon.se/websimon-tables.
